style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">ou desatualizados.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>4. A exclus\u00e3o de seus Dados Coletados na hip\u00f3tese de t\u00e9rmino da rela\u00e7\u00e3o <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">comercial, salvo situa\u00e7\u00f5es em que exista a obriga\u00e7\u00e3o de guarda e comprova\u00e7\u00e3o <\/span><span style=\"color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">do seguro obedecendo ao prazo previsto em legisla\u00e7\u00e3o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>5. A exclus\u00e3o de seus Dados Coletados a qualquer tempo, salvo situa\u00e7\u00f5es em que <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">exista a obriga\u00e7\u00e3o de guarda e comprova\u00e7\u00e3o do seguro obedecendo ao prazo <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); f