font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">na qualidade de titular dos Dados Coletados pela Vila Velha, declara estar ciente <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">dos termos e condi\u00e7\u00f5es descrita no presente Termo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>O Cliente ou Segurado\/Benefici\u00e1rio aceita plenamente, livre e espontaneamente a <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Coleta, Manuten\u00e7\u00e3o e Tratamentos de seus dados pela Vila Velha.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>O Cliente ou Segurado\/Benefici\u00e1rio autoriza a Vila Velha isoladamente ou em <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">conjunto com as Companhias Seguradoras a realizarem, na forma da lei vigente, o <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">tratamento dos seus dados coletados, a serem utilizados e compartilhados <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">especificamente para as finalidades descritas neste Termo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>4. VIG\u00caNCIA<\/b><\/p>\n<p>A autoriza\u00e7\u00e3o concedida neste Termo tem dura\u00e7\u00e3o relacionada \u00e0 vig\u00eancia dos <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Seguros contratados. <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Findada a vig\u00eancia dos seguros, os dados coletados ficar\u00e3o armazenados em <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">nosso banco de dados pelo per\u00edodo previsto na legisla\u00e7\u00e3o que regulada cada um <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">dos seguros.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>5. DISPOSI\u00c7\u00d5ES GERAIS<\/b><\/p>\n<p>As condi\u00e7\u00f5es previstas neste Termo poder\u00e3o ser atualizadas a qualquer tempo <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">pela Vila Velha, devendo, para tanto, o Segurado\/Benefici\u00e1rio ser prontamente <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">informado sobre tais atualiza\u00e7\u00f5es.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>O n\u00e3o exerc\u00edcio de quaisquer direitos ou faculdades que sejam conferidos \u00e0 Partes <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">por este Termo ou pela legisla\u00e7\u00e3o brasileira, n\u00e3o importar\u00e1 na ren\u00fancia aos seus <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 25