etar\u00e1 dados pessoais necess\u00e1rios ao relacionamento <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">comercial e realiza\u00e7\u00e3o de cota\u00e7\u00e3o de seguros.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>A Vila Velha \u00e9 a corretora dos \u201cSeguros\u201d:<\/p>\n<p>(i) Seguro de Vida;<\/p>\n<p>(ii) Seguro Sa\u00fade;<\/p>\n<p>(iii) Assist\u00eancia M\u00e9dico-hospitalar.<\/p>\n<p>Durante a contrata\u00e7\u00e3o dos Seguros, poder\u00e1 ser solicitada a Declara\u00e7\u00e3o de Sa\u00fade <span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">do Segurado\/Benefici\u00e1rio e, dependendo do seguro, de seus dependentes. Essa <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">declara\u00e7\u00e3o poder\u00e1 conter o hist\u00f3rico de doen\u00e7as, interven\u00e7\u00f5es cir\u00fargicas, doen\u00e7as <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">pr\u00e9-existentes e heredit\u00e1rias e eventuais relat\u00f3rios m\u00e9dicos complementares. <\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing);\">Situa\u00e7\u00e3o legalmente prevista para a aceita\u00e7\u00e3o do seguro. <\/span><span style=\"color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">Nessa ocasi\u00e3o, a Vila Velha ser\u00e1 exclusivamente a intermedi\u00e1ria para a solicita\u00e7\u00e3o e <\/span><span style=\"color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">envio das declara\u00e7\u00f5es, n\u00e3o armazenando nenhuma informa\u00e7\u00e3o em seu banco de <\/span><span style=\"color: var(--body_typography-color); font-family: var(--body_typography-font-family); font-size: var(--body_typography-font-size); font-style: var(--body_typography-font-style,normal); font-weight: var(--body_typography-font-weight); letter-spacing: var(--body_typography-letter-spacing); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">dados.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>1.1.FINALIDADE DA COLETA E TRATAMENTO DE DADOS PESSOAIS<\/b><\/p>\n<p>A Vila Velha pontualmente coleta dados pes